Class java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap

Added interface java.io.Serializable.

Added Constructors
ConcurrentHashMap(int, float, int) Creates a new, empty map with an initial table size based on the given number of elements ({@code initialCapacity}), table density ({@code loadFactor}), and number of concurrently updating threads ({@code concurrencyLevel}).
